metadata.name: Bad Ass Doge #1730
metadata.description: They were summoned in from the DOGVERSE. Upon discovery, we realized each dog had completely different characteristics and traits. Our scientists took months to analyze these clans BioMech Junkies - UnGovernable War Dogs - Stellar Outcasts - CosmoPawlitans -M1sfts. But then they soon realized that even those clans had fusioned creating traits impossible to understand!
